OL,3,CPlans for #65m 'amusement centre'
OL,4,Capproved by city council
OL,6,FPlans have been approved for a #65
OL,7,Fmillion project that aims to create an
OL,8,F"amusement centre" in Newcastle city
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FA major redevelopment at Newcastle's
OL,12,Fflagship shopping centre has been
OL,13,Fgiven the green light by city council
OL,14,Fplanners.
OL,16,FThe proposals for Eldon Square will
OL,17,Fbring new leisure, culture and dining
OL,18,Ffacilities to Newcastle City Centre.
