OL,4,Capproved by city council
OL,6,FIt is hoped the changes will attract
OL,7,Fnew visitors, bring millions into the
OL,8,Fcity's economy and create hundreds of
OL,9,Fjobs.
OL,11,FWhat will the plans include?
OL,13,FTwo new cultural, food and drink,
OL,14,Fsport, leisure and entertainment
OL,15,Fvenues will be added to Eldon Square.
