OL,3,CPlans for #65m 'amusement centre'
OL,4,Capproved by city council
OL,6,FThe proposals, first revealed in
OL,7,FDecember, were brought forward after
OL,8,Fthe closure of big-name retailers
OL,9,Fincluding Debenhams, which left
OL,10,Fthousands of square feet in the
OL,11,Fshopping centre empty.
OL,13,FA council meeting on 12 April heard
OL,14,Fplanning officers blame the increase
OL,15,Fin vacant lots on changes in shopping
OL,16,Fhabits, accelerated by the Covid
OL,17,Fpandemic.
