OL,3,CPlans for #65m 'amusement centre'
OL,4,Capproved by city council
OL,6,FCouncillors were told that the plans
OL,7,Ffor the former Debenhams site would
OL,8,Fcreate 350 new jobs, bring in #11.24
OL,9,Fmillion into the city's economy, and
OL,10,Fattract an additional 780,000 visitors.
OL,12,FThe Eldon Leisure plans are expected
OL,13,Fto create a further 210 jobs and bring
OL,14,Fin #8.84 million to the local economy.
