OL,6,FSpeaking after the meeting, the city
OL,7,Fcouncil's director of growth and
OL,8,Finvestment, Michelle Percy, said: "The
OL,9,Fcouncil's vision for Newcastle city
OL,10,Fcentre is a place that is economically
OL,11,Fstrong, inclusive, and sustainable in
OL,12,Fwhich residents can be proud.
OL,14,F"This #65m of new investment in Eldon
OL,15,FSquare is proof of the diversification
OL,16,Fof the city centre providing a boost
OL,17,Fto culture, leisure and entertainment
OL,18,Foffering live music, dance, and
OL,19,Fperformances.
